{"data":[{"type":"questionAttempts","id":"17620494","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/questionAttempts/17620494"},"attributes":{"position":0,"marks":1,"score":1,"answeredAt":"2025-09-30T15:43:08+09:30","options":[1],"response":null,"finalizedAt":"2025-09-30T15:43:08+09:30"},"relationships":{"user":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"50098"}},"questionSession":{"data":null},"session":{"data":null},"question":{"data":{"type":"questions","id":"16630"}},"bookmark":{"data":null}}}],"included":[{"type":"questions","id":"16630","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/questions/16630"},"attributes":{"optionProportions":[0,0.68,0.04,0.24,0.04]},"relationships":{"item":{"data":{"type":"items","id":"9321"}},"activeRevision":{"data":{"type":"questionRevisions","id":"68408"}}}},{"type":"items","id":"9321","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/items/9321"},"attributes":{"contentType":"question","status":"accepted","createdAt":"2024-11-29T09:52:29+10:30","updatedAt":"2024-12-10T09:48:25+10:30","updatedAction":"commented","acceptedAt":"2024-12-09T17:05:58+10:30","editorNotifiedAt":null,"feedbackAt":"2025-09-29 15:08:48"},"relationships":{"content":{"data":{"type":"questions","id":"16630"}},"updatedBy":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"9"}},"author":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"7912"}},"activeRevision":{"data":{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"53865"}},"tags":{"data":[{"type":"tags","id":"67"},{"type":"tags","id":"71"},{"type":"tags","id":"74"},{"type":"tags","id":"4935"},{"type":"tags","id":"4943"},{"type":"tags","id":"4947"},{"type":"tags","id":"5306"}]},"contributions":{"data":[{"type":"contributions","id":"22094"},{"type":"contributions","id":"22909"},{"type":"contributions","id":"23025"}]},"lastContribution":{"data":null},"lastRevision":{"data":{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"53865"}},"lastActivity":{"data":null},"lastFeedback":{"data":null}},"meta":{"canRevise":false,"canManage":false,"canDelete":false}},{"type":"questionRevisions","id":"68408","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/questionRevisions/68408"},"attributes":{"stem":"\u003Cp\u003EA 22-year-old woman presents to the sexual health clinic requesting advice about contraception. She reports using condoms but has experienced several breakages during intercourse. On further questioning, she mentions using moisturising cream as a lubricant.\u003C/p\u003E","stemQuestion":"Which one of the following best describes the likely cause of the condom failures?","responseType":"sba","marks":1,"options":["Silicone-based lubricant degradation","Chemical degradation from oil-based moisturiser","Latex protein denaturation from friction","Glycerin-induced polymer breakdown","Structural weakening from heat exposure"],"correctOptions":[1],"correctResponses":null,"explanation":"\u003Cp\u003EThe condom failures are likely due to \u003Cstrong\u003Echemical degradation from oil-based moisturiser\u003C/strong\u003E. Oil-based products including moisturising creams, petroleum jelly, and mineral oils rapidly degrade latex condoms, significantly increasing the risk of breakage.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe other suggested causes are less likely:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESilicone-based lubricant degradation\u003C/strong\u003E - Silicone-based lubricants are specifically designed to be safe with latex condoms\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELatex protein denaturation from friction\u003C/strong\u003E - While friction can cause wear, it does not typically cause rapid condom failure\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGlycerin-induced polymer breakdown\u003C/strong\u003E - Glycerin is commonly used in water-based lubricants and does not degrade latex\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EStructural weakening from heat exposure\u003C/strong\u003E - Normal body temperature does not cause significant latex degradation\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOnly water-based or silicone-based lubricants should be used with latex condoms. Oil-based products can cause condom failure within minutes of exposure.\u003C/p\u003E","optionExplanations":["","","","",""],"learningPoints":["Latex condoms are effective barriers against sexually transmitted infections including HIV, hepatitis B, and herpes simplex virus.","Oil-based lubricants degrade latex condoms and significantly increase the risk of condom failure.","Water-based and silicone-based lubricants are safe to use with latex condoms."],"references":["Crosby R, Sanders S, Yarber WL, Graham CA. Condom-use errors and problems: a neglected aspect of studies assessing condom effectiveness. Am J Prev Med. 2003;24(4):367-370. doi:10.1016/s0749-3797(03)00015-1","Kim M, McKenney J, Khosropour CM, et al. Factors Associated With Condom Breakage During Anal Intercourse: A Cross-Sectional Study of Men Who Have Sex With Men Recruited in an Online Survey. JMIR Public Health Surveill. 2016;2(1):e7. Published 2016 Feb 22. doi:10.2196/publichealth.5298"]},"relationships":{"itemRevision":{"data":{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"53865"}},"question":{"data":{"type":"questions","id":"16630"}},"stemMedia":{"data":[]},"explanationMedia":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"53865","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/itemRevisions/53865"},"attributes":{"createdAt":"2024-12-09T17:04:31+10:30","updatedAt":"2024-12-09T17:05:19+10:30","number":5,"notes":"","plagiarismCheckedAt":"2024-12-09T17:04:35+10:30","plagiarismScore":11.4,"plagiarismReportUrl":"https://emedici-copyleaks.syd1.digitaloceanspaces.com/plagiarism-report-9321-5.pdf?X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=DO00QAKVE68N83EBLT2J%2F20250930%2Fsyd1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20250930T061308Z\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026X-Amz-Expires=601200\u0026X-Amz-Signature=87a5bd80e58cb87e1cb3af6d259203ec1c381b92c2cf24e6cef8312a5bf55735"},"relationships":{"item":{"data":{"type":"items","id":"9321"}},"content":{"data":{"type":"questionRevisi